title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 9, subtit. Q, ch. VI, pt. 599 - Repealed
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 9, subtit. Q, ch. VI, pt. 599 - Repealed

State Regulations

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 9, subtit. Q, ch. VI, pt. 599

Parts 600 through 1260 of Title 9 NYCRR were repealed on

July 3, 2002, effective on January 1, 2003. Historical information concerning
sections found in these Parts are available from the Division of Administrative

Rules of the Department of State. Parts 1280, 1281, 1282, 1300, 1350 and 1400 were renumbered
as: Title 19 Parts 1260, 1209, 1261, 1262; Title 9, Part 2651; and Title 19

Part 1263 respectively in October 2002. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
